      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/242670-self-portrait-in-a-convex-mirror">Quotes from Self-Portrait in ...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;The summer demands and takes away too much. /But night, the reserved, the reticent, gives more than it takes&rdquo;</span>
